+  font-size:0.8em;opacity:.9;}                                                  /* printer's fleuron ❦ */
+
+/* ---- signature element: gold-leaf bridges ----
+   the ★ cross-domain bridges become inlaid gold leaf — a matte gilt line with
+   a fine dark under-edge that reads as raised, hand-laid gold, instead of neon
